title: Look After
description: Social media can sometimes be a toxic environment. Without proper attention, friends and family can be consumed by the compiled negativity. This application aims to take a deeper look at the users emotions and personality while pointing out instances where they may not have been healthy in conversation. Look After tries to promote healthy conversation by providing a URL to the users messages. In development we used ASP.net MVC in combination with the Twitter API and the Google Natural Language Processing API. We also used multiple studies and datasets based on the big 5 personality traits and 6 emotions to analyze and interpret the data returned from the APIs.
tech: ASP.net, C#, Google-cloud-language, javascript, mvc, twitterAPI, Bootstrap

title: Neurosergery Website
description: My team and I developed a web app for the UF Neurosurgery department to allow patients and admins to request, view, and add appointments. The app allows patients to create an account, view upcoming appointments and reminders, view contact and clinic location information, and request new appointments. The app also allows admins to create an account, view current patient and appointment information, approve appointments, and create new appointments. (You may log on to the test site with the email: admin@admin.com and password: admin for admin or email: test@test.com and password: test for general user)
tech: MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js, ANT Design, CRUD, Crypto, node-cron, Google Maps API, Mailgun and twilio

title: Twitter Tweet Tracker
description: Twitter Tweet Tracker takes in tweet and follower data from individuals and generates a five-personality model, six emotion model, subjectivity bar, frequency table, and various tweet charts. This application is deisgned to identify at risk or unsable twitter users. Using word analysis and key context clues, we can create a model of a twitter user who might be experiencing distress and other abnormal emotional spikes. Because of the rapid nature of twitter, it can be hard for individuals to keep track of their friends when they need them the most. Thus, this application can help users in keeping up with their friends over larger periods of time.
